why don't you show it today?

14
00:00:40,880 --> 00:00:42,400
She's angry.

15
00:00:42,760 --> 00:00:44,600
Make sure you show it this time.

16
00:00:45,360 --> 00:00:48,040
Their journey will mainly be
in Saga Prefecture

17
00:00:48,120 --> 00:00:49,480
where glass art thrives,

18
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:51,880
and will also go to hot springs
as Madame wishes,

19
00:00:52,040 --> 00:00:54,840
and travel around Oita Prefecture,
all in this journey.

20
00:00:55,120 --> 00:00:56,840
Also, starting this time...

21
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:59,360
- New girl, Yokota will join.
- That's right.

22
00:00:59,440 --> 00:01:02,400
It was tough enough
when Yumeppe joined the other day.

23
00:01:02,480 --> 00:01:04,240
If Yokota also joins,

24
00:01:04,320 --> 00:01:05,960
