26
00:01:08,320 --> 00:01:09,640
- We've told her.
- You have?

27
00:01:09,720 --> 00:01:10,800
What did you say?

28
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:13,200
A new girl called Yokota
will come this time.

29
00:01:13,360 --> 00:01:16,160
Is that so? Why don't you
reduce the number a bit?

30
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:18,800
Mayuko will leave first.

31
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:23,480
What will the girls' gathering
this time be like?

32
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:33,160
Welcome to The Quest.

33
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:36,560
Today's programme is
Degawa Girls Gathering Special.

34
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,560
Wasshoi!

35
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,600
"Morisanchu"

36
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:39,560
Hello...

37
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:40,600
Hello!

38
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:41,600
Hello, everyone!

39
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,560
"Madame Dewi"

40
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,560
"Mayuko Kawakita, Akane Hotta"

41
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,600
"Yumena Yanai, Mayuu Yokota"

42
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:47,720
Mr Advisor, it's an hour
of girls gathering again?

43
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:48,640
One hour.

44
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:49,720
Thank you.

45
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:52,800
We're really happy,

46
