00:28:02,280 --> 00:28:04,080
We have to carry it already?

647
00:28:04,160 --> 00:28:05,600
Carry it upstream, get on it.

648
00:28:05,680 --> 00:28:08,120
We'll repeat the process
till we're there.

649
00:28:08,200 --> 00:28:09,240
That's tough.

